flowchart LR
    U[RSU Student] --> WEB[RSU Nexus Frontend]
    ADMIN[Authorized Admin] --> WEB

    V[Vercel Hosting] --> WEB
    WEB --> AUTH[Supabase Authentication]
    WEB --> DB[(Supabase PostgreSQL)]
    WEB --> STORAGE[(Supabase Storage)]

    WEB --> HOME[Homepage and Navigation]
    WEB --> MARKET[Browse / Search / Filter]
    WEB --> FORM[Create Listing and Request Forms]
    WEB --> DETAIL[Listing Detail and Status]
    WEB --> DASH[Dashboard / My Listings]
    WEB --> ADMINP[Protected Admin View]

    FORM --> DB
    FORM --> STORAGE
    DB --> MARKET
    DB --> DETAIL
    DB --> DASH
    ADMINP --> DB

    RLS[Row Level Security Policies] --> DB
    RLS --> STORAGE
